text: Mukachevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Isimovsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 149 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Mrakovo, 8 km from Isimovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Mukachevo, Kugarchinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
